Package ohos.data.rdb

Class DataObserverAsyncWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.rdb.DataObserverAsyncWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataObserver

    public class DataObserverAsyncWrapper
extends Object
implements DataObserver
    A wrapper class of DataObserver. The DataObserverAsyncWrapper instance notifies the wrapped DataObserver instance asynchronously.

    The observer is used as an input parameter for the ResultSet.registerObserver(ohos.data.rdb.DataObserver) and ResultSet.unregisterObserver(ohos.data.rdb.DataObserver) methods.

    Since:
    3
